item.title: [help] can someone help me with this thing that i found
item.dc:creator: @Ron Ron
item.description:
@Ron wrote:

I went there, and then enabled javascript, and it worked. I didn’t like it cause I had to Ctrl Alt Del firefox. If people don’t have javascript enabled you should add this after the tag.

<noscript>
Please enable javascript, or this website won't work, and you won't be able to check out the stuff on this website!
</noscript>

If they don’t have javascript enabled it will say:

Please enable javascript, or this website won’t work, and you won’t be able to check out the stuff on this website!

~Ron
